<h2 id=3D"CreditTransferDataMatrix-CreditTransfer">Credit Transfer</h2>
<p>The table below maps the end-to-end data flow from portal to submission =
for a payment request, including all FIS components, Service Mesh, and 10x.=
&nbsp;</p>
<h3 id=3D"CreditTransferDataMatrix-FSIS">FSIS</h3>
<p>For fraud and sanctions, we pass on the full messages via the Partner AP=
I and that's why it doesn't make sense to include any detailed mapping from=
 POM/NPP Product to these components.</p>
<p>At this point in time&nbsp;<time datetime=3D"2025-05-14" class=3D"date-p=
ast">14 May 2025</time>&nbsp; we haven't done any detailed mapping for PRM =
as to what they would like to receive from POM. When we do then the mapping=
 from the pain.001 will get included be included in the data matrix.&nbsp;<=
/p>
<p>NRV expects the pacs.008 to be provided in it's entirety and for that re=
ason the mapping to NRV hasn't been included, as to what they use from the =
pacs.008 is internal to their system.&nbsp;</p>
